reviewText: If you are a real beginner, you may get a helping hand on the process. If you aren't save your money and time.

Hugely disappointing! Even a giant stretch of the imagination could not warrant calling this a "Design Instructional". It is nothing more than an exercise in how to stick transfer film. If you've ever used scotch tape you can do without this DVD. I tried to contact the author via her website several times, to no avail.
